{# The cutaway house shell: walls, roof, living room, utility recess. The roof
   itself is a plain solid gable (no cutaway) so solar panels have a single
   unambiguous surface to sit flush on. The `insulation` prop (0|1|2) drives
   the visible wall insulation layer locally; roof snow, room tint and
   chimney smoke follow scene-wide ambience classes. #}
{% props insulation = 0 %}
<g class="house house--ins-{{ insulation }}"{{ attributes }}>{{ include('game/scene/assets/house-cutaway.svg') }}</g>
